{"tid":543092,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做老闆真係要有道德呀，原來真係有報應架","createTime":"2018-01-28T06:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T17:36:35.000Z","uid":17248,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22e132d6c2a44bea96036881b37c0c6ba824e8bc","tid":543092,"uid":17248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"話說小弟之前起尖沙咀一間台式飲品鋪做啦<br />\n邊條街同邊間唔講啦因爲唔係好多間廢是自爆<br />\n之後個老闆成日都好唔滿意我唔夠快架啦<br />\n之後除夕倒數無人肯番工佢叫我番啦<br />\n咁好啦我番啦<br />\n仆佢個臭街倒數完嗰晚之後番完幾日就叫我走<br />\n話番埋今個星期唔洗再叫我番<br />\n之後我嬲到仆街<br />\n我最後起佢隔離既鋪揾左份長工<br />\n仲做得好開心<br />\n佢把口其實都賤架啦<br />\n成日串隔離啲台式飲品鋪生意唔夠佢好串人地好得閒<br />\n但哩排開始起佢附近開多左兩間台式飲品鋪<br />\n佢啲生意就唔洗我多講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多時經過見到佢無生意得一兩個客<br />\n個心真係涼<br />\n就連之前成日比佢串既隔離嗰間生意都好過佢<br />\n用完我即棄呀嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵撚你死無生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日講到自己間野幾威幾威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我日日起你隔離睇到你無乜生意真係心都涼曬<br />\n所以哩個世界真係有報應架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人在做天在看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f6d360b2bb497a0fe78db301cd95d02f186e65","tid":543092,"uid":62337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"台式飲品店老闆都可以打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b665c3960e4223436769ff57d82416c65a8961f2","tid":543092,"uid":12158,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e2f6d360b2bb497a0fe78db301cd95d02f186e65","tid":543092,"uid":6233